source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_00<tab>Etgar requires your assistance with a raptor predicament.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_00<tab>ワインポートのエトガルは、冒険者に魔物の討伐を頼みたいようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_01<tab>Etgar, a local tender of Wineport's vineyards, has requested your assistance with a grass raptor problem. The scalekin have been munching on the outpost's precious vines, and they must be stopped. Track down four of the beasts and teach them a lesson.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_01<tab>ワインポート周辺で暴れまわっている「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2019B01 /var>」を退治してほしいらしい。<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2019B01 /var>を4匹討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_02<tab>You have shown a quartet of raptors what for, and made the vineyards safe for another day. Report your success to Etgar.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2019B01 /var>を討伐した。ワインポートの「エトガル」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_03<tab>Etgar seems well pleased by your tidings, and vows to keep you in mind should he have need of your services in the future.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_SEQ_03<tab>冒険者の活躍にエトガルは満足したようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_ETGAR_000_000<tab>Hallo, adventurer! Hear me, or Master Byrglaent will know the reason why! I mean that he'll simply tell you himself if you refuse to hear it from <var 1A 02 /var>me<var 1A 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_ETGAR_000_000ビルギレント様の愛弟子である私の話を聞いてくだされば、
あとで便宜を図らないでもないですよぉ？

source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_ETGAR_000_001<tab>You've no doubt seen those ghastly grass raptors skulking about outside our gates. Well, they've developed a taste for the vines we use to grow our brandewine cherries, and we can't abide that. You <var 1A 02 /var>must<var 1A 01 /var> kill the horrible creatures!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_ETGAR_000_001そうですねぇ～、ワインポート周辺で暴れまわっている
「」を退治してきてほしいですねぇ。
アイツらが畑に来たら、仕事どころじゃなくなりますしぃ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_ETGAR_000_020<tab>Ah, the conquering <var 08 E905 ((heroine)) ((hero)) /var> returns! And so quickly, too. You are as strong as you are kind, and <var 08 E905 ((pleasingly made about the shoulders)) ((wonderfully trim of waist)) /var>. I shall make sure to keep you in mind should any future troubles creep up.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB210_00841_ETGAR_000_020ありがとうございますぅ。
いやぁ～、冒険者さんは、お強いですねぇ。
ご活躍は、ビルギレント様にお伝えしておきますねぇ。
